page.name: Jack's Rage
page.description: This sword was used by a pumpkin golem given life by ancient magic. It fought for good, and defended the innocent, until it finally fell in battle, and was bound to its weapons by an evil sorcerer.

page.name: Jack's Carver
page.description: As a being of pumpkins and vines, Jack was able to wield many weapons at once. Those that survived its onslaught would recount that it used many of these smaller blades in a thrashing fury.

page.name: Jack's Spire
page.description: Every year, attempts are made to remake Jack- for good or ill. None have ever come close. Perhaps some ingredient is missing.
